me":"2018-10-17T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"巴打，我好明白你既感受<br />\n我地依加一齊感受緊<br />\n你並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc7ef9568b5a7fcf045d2f8e5ae45b63bb0ebeb","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e1383c13a87f4cbb4721b8055a1274e244da3b","tid":866191,"uid":215675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560874a27fe2e74d96ed8d4ba0a7d65559798639","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c04fe0160e950ac2c0e95474dc4bbbb39e0a1982","tid":866191,"uid":215675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔好食呀，雖然一時麻醉到自己<br />\n由其是搵到一個方法/地方/人 解決到一啲野<br />\n但要戒果時就好痛苦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"如果無錢就戒到當然最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我屋企窮果時，阿媽會係自己個煙灰缸搵下有無食剩既煙頭點返著再食。果時個畫面印左係我個腦海度<br />\n中三之後決定唔再讀書，出去返份工補貼下阿媽<br />\n我想講既係，無錢果時可能會好似我阿媽咁要去止癮<br />\n所以無習慣食既話，希望唔好再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f01fe5d4540b0f7feca46165e91dbe68b2bb14a","tid":866191,"uid":215675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3737a1650ab8eb5cc9751a862c95fbd9131d9a8","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2aaf5dcc054ff003bc70a80c128fed31d7348ac","tid":866191,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b59d05aa185c7fb4b3a4baa1dee2a48489b43a2","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a73fb324212a9bbe233a12f0b31c6232857b9dd7","tid":866191,"uid":104218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"你無食返啲精當然沒用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"食過，甜既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:17:03.000Z","msg