"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb0a38490276e375ff954372b6117f7e29e3e731","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2edd6daeb5a6114bb961ad9ea2b007d5741c054","tid":866191,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"呢種感覺而家就經歷緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊太多嘢煩 就算有人陪你傾幾句計<br />\n都係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無力感好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"你諗下唔止你一個人有依種感受<br />\n諗完之黎就會發覺自己並不孤單<br />\n因為有我地依班人一齊同時感受緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"多謝清先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排屋企好多嘢煩 個人都變得神經質咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"快手咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想離開屋企逃避下<br />\n但又唔想唔理兩老就咁走咗去<br />\n特別係呢段時間兩老一直都好多support <br />\n唔捨得一走了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但好多時一自己一個留喺屋企就會開始亂諗嘢<br />\n好多擔憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c8558a230526d66c1a71d7054db771a91dc08c","tid":866191,"uid":49457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"的確好難受，但你又搵唔到人講<br />\n又自己消除唔到le種寂寞感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840fef7edacc2214976ee385aaae4f95fa44ad75","tid":866191,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce04d0a1d38007b96d4ab96bef97c3723eccd89","tid":866191,"uid":207462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3312d061f77ea5951532933fe2a9b1d69e0dc33a","tid":866191,"uid":207462